{"data":[{"name":"80:1","price":"[¡Oh, Mujámmad!] Frunciste el ceño y le diste la espalda","arabic":"عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5759,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:2","price":"al ciego cuando se presentó ante ti.","arabic":"أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلۡأَعۡمَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5760,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"Referencia a cuando ‘Abdullah Ibn Umm Maktum, que era ciego, interrumpió al Profeta, que la paz y las bendiciones de Dios sean con él, que estaba predicando el Islam a los nobles de la tribu de Quraish.","lang":"es"},{"name":"80:3","price":"¿Cómo sabes que no quería purificarse [aprendiendo de ti el conocimiento],","arabic":"وَمَا يُدۡرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5761,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:4","price":"o beneficiarse con tus enseñanzas?","arabic":"أَوۡ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5762,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:5","price":"En cambio, al soberbio","arabic":"أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5763,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:6","price":"le dedicaste toda tu atención.","arabic":"فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5764,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:7","price":"Pero tú no eres responsable si él rechaza purificarse [de la idolatría, ya que tu obligación solo es transmitir el Mensaje].","arabic":"وَمَا عَلَيۡكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5765,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:8","price":"En cambio, aquel que se presentó ante ti con deseos [de aprender],","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5766,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:9","price":"teniendo temor de Dios,","arabic":"وَهُوَ يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5767,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:10","price":"te apartaste de él.","arabic":"فَأَنتَ عَنۡهُ تَلَهَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5768,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:11","price":"No lo vuelvas a hacer, porque este Mensaje es para toda la humanidad.","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذۡكِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5769,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:12","price":"Quien quiera, que reflexione y obre acorde a él.","arabic":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5770,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:13","price":"Pues el Mensaje está registrado en páginas honorables,","arabic":"فِي صُحُفٖ مُّكَرَّمَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5771,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:14","price":"distinguidas y purificadas,","arabic":"مَّرۡفُوعَةٖ مُّطَهَّرَةِۭ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5772,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:15","price":"en manos de [ángeles] encargados de ejecutar las órdenes de Dios,","arabic":"بِأَيۡدِي سَفَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5773,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:16","price":"nobles y obedientes.","arabic":"كِرَامِۭ بَرَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5774,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:17","price":"El ser humano se destruye a sí mismo con su ingratitud.","arabic":"قُتِلَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَآ أَكۡفَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5775,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:18","price":"¿Acaso no sabe de qué ha sido creado?","arabic":"مِنۡ أَيِّ شَيۡءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5776,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:19","price":"De un óvulo fecundado, que crece en etapas según lo [que Él ha] establecido.","arabic":"مِن نُّطۡفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5777,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:20","price":"Luego le facilita el camino.","arabic":"ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5778,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:21","price":"Luego lo hace morir y ser enterrado.","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُۥ فَأَقۡبَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5779,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:22","price":"Finalmente lo resucita cuando Él quiere.","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِذَا شَآءَ أَنشَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5780,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:23","price":"Pero a pesar de esto no cumple con los preceptos que se le ordenan.","arabic":"كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقۡضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5781,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:24","price":"El ser humano debería reflexionar sobre su alimento:","arabic":"فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5782,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:25","price":"Hice descender el agua en abundancia,","arabic":"أَنَّا صَبَبۡنَا ٱلۡمَآءَ صَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5783,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:26","price":"luego hice que la tierra brotara.","arabic":"ثُمَّ شَقَقۡنَا ٱلۡأَرۡضَ شَقّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5784,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:27","price":"Hice surgir de ella granos,","arabic":"فَأَنۢبَتۡنَا فِيهَا حَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5785,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:28","price":"vides, hierbas,","arabic":"وَعِنَبٗا وَقَضۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5786,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:29","price":"olivos, palmeras,","arabic":"وَزَيۡتُونٗا وَنَخۡلٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5787,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:30","price":"huertos frondosos,","arabic":"وَحَدَآئِقَ غُلۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5788,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:31","price":"frutos y forraje","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٗ وَأَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5789,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:32","price":"para beneficio de ustedes y de sus rebaños.","arabic":"مَّتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5790,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:33","price":"El día que llegue el estruendo terrible [comenzando el fin del mundo],","arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلصَّآخَّةُ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5791,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:34","price":"el ser humano huirá de su hermano,","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَفِرُّ ٱلۡمَرۡءُ مِنۡ أَخِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5792,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:35","price":"de su madre y de su padre,","arabic":"وَأُمِّهِۦ وَأَبِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5793,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:36","price":"de su esposa y de sus hijos.","arabic":"وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَبَنِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5794,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:37","price":"Ese día cada uno estará preocupado por sí mismo.","arabic":"لِكُلِّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ شَأۡنٞ يُغۡنِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5795,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:38","price":"Ese día habrá rostros radiantes,","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ مُّسۡفِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5796,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:39","price":"risueños y felices [por haber alcanzado la salvación].","arabic":"ضَاحِكَةٞ مُّسۡتَبۡشِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5797,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:40","price":"Pero habrá otros rostros ensombrecidos,","arabic":"وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَلَيۡهَا غَبَرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5798,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:41","price":"apesadumbrados [por haber merecido la condena al Infierno].","arabic":"تَرۡهَقُهَا قَتَرَةٌ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5799,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"80:42","price":"Esos serán los que rechazaron el Mensaje y los transgresores [de la ley].","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡكَفَرَةُ ٱلۡفَجَرَةُ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5800,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"}],"chapter":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa","Chapter Abasa","Surah 80","Chapter 80","He Frowned","عبس"]}